members.name: NavigatorID.appCodeName
members.description: Always returns 'Mozilla', on any browser. This property is kept only for compatibility purpose.

members.name: NavigatorID.appName
members.description: Returns the official name of the browser. Do not rely on this property to return the correct value.

members.name: NavigatorID.appVersion
members.description: Returns the version of the browser as a string. Do not rely on this property to return the correct value.

members.name: NavigatorID.platform
members.description: Returns a string representing the platform of the browser. Do not rely on this property to return the correct value.

members.name: NavigatorID.product
members.description: Always returns 'Gecko', on any browser. This property is kept only for compatibility purpose.

members.name: NavigatorID.userAgent
members.description: Returns the user agent string for the current browser.

members.name: NavigatorID.taintEnabled()
members.description: Always returns false. JavaScript taint/untaint functions were removed in JavaScript 1.2. This method is only kept for compatibility purpose
